St James Properties LLC, Marina Office

data.description: Welcome to your coastal oasis in the  Beaver Creek section of St. James Plantation in Southport. As you approach, you'll be greeted by a lovely crepe myrtle adorning the front lawn, a testament to the property's timeless beauty & heritage. The meticulously crafted home seamlessly blends low country charm with modern elegance, offering a haven of  both comfort  & style.A welcoming rocking chair front porch sets the stage for relaxation, while inside, the heart of the home awaits. Step into this inviting living room bathed in natural light, where warmth emanates from the rich tones of the wood floors. The focal point, a cozy gas fireplace, adds charm & functionality, inviting relaxation on chilly evenings. A  renovated kitchen features semi-custom cabinets, granite countertops, & stainless steel appliances, creating a perfect space for culinary gatherings.The adjacent dining room, with its new light fixture & sliders lead to the screened-in porch offering a serene spot to enjoy coastal breezes. Retreat to the primary suite, where luxury awaits with  custom built-ins , walk in closet & an attached ensuite boasting a tiled shower, newer vanity w/vessel sinks, & a full-length mirror.At the back of the home is a powder room &  separate shower ideal for washing up after a day at the beach.Ascend the staircase to discover a spacious bonus room, complete with wall-to-wall carpeting & access to attic storage. This versatile space offers endless possibilities, from a  bedroom, to a home office, media room or playroom.The main staircase leads to 2 additional large bedrooms, each with ample closet space & attic access, providing comfortable accommodations for family or guests. A remodeled full bath, featuring a huge tub & vessel sinks, adds a touch of luxury. With access to world-class amenities including golf courses, a marina, walking trails, & private beach club, St James offers the ultimate coastal lifestyle. Don't miss your chance to call  this residence home
